            "title": "滬指開市升13點 深成指升121點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段造好，上證綜指以3251點開市，升13點或0.42%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報9955點，更漲121點或1.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升21點或0.57%，開報3772點；創業板指數開市報1954點，升27點或1.44%。</p>\n</div>",
