        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段續隨外圍反彈 恒指開升449點報21363點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">儘管美國總統特朗普昨天宣稱對等關稅根本沒有「豁免 」，共是轉移至另一類別關稅，但投資市場仍憧憬關稅戰緩和，推動股市反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">繼華爾街股市上周五揚升後，亞洲主要股市今早造好，港股於競價時段亦跟漲。恒生指數開市報21363點，升449點或2.15%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5053點，升153點或3.13%；國企指數以7970點開市，升168點或2.16%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股進一步反彈，阿里巴巴(09988)開報107.4元，升4.27%；騰訊(00700)開報453元，升2.17%；美團(03690)開報146.6元，升2.16%；京東(09618)的ADR上周五晚逆市向下，股份今早在港則開報145元，升1.33%；小米(01810)開報45.2元，升2.15%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大重磅金融股均造好，滙控(00005)開報77.2元，升2.25%；友邦(01299)開報51.55元，升2.79%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國人民保險(01339)與旗下中國財險(02328)先後發盈喜，兩股今早均向好。中國人保開報3.93元，升2.08%；財險開報13.76元，升1.58%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國人民保險官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230724_FI_source-web_01339.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國人民保險官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230724_FI_source-web_01339.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國人民保險官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">正力新能(03677)今日登場，開報8.46元，較招股價8.27元高2.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鳳祥股份(09977)獲以33.33%溢價提私有化，該股今早復牌開報1.88元，漲25.33%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14852346-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e7%ba%8c%e9%9a%a8%e5%a4%96%e5%9c%8d%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%8d%87449%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121363%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKS_source-bp_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-14 09:31:05",
            "source": "bastillepost",
